title: Orange Cyberdefense
description:
This connector allows to ingest into OpenCTI the Cyber Threat Intelligence provided by the CERT Orange CyberDefense.
Depending on its configuration and your subscription level it will ingest Indicators, Reports, Vulnerabilities, Intrusion Set, Malwares, ...
short_description: This connector allows to ingest into OpenCTI the Cyber Threat Intelligence provided by the CERT Orange Cyberdefense.
